# Docker 部署仓库白名单：默认忽略全部，只放行构建和运行需要的源码、配置、依赖清单与 Docker 入口。

*
!*/

# 根目录 Docker 部署入口和依赖清单
!/.gitignore
!/.dockerignore
!/.npmrc
!/.env.example
!/docker-compose.yml
!/Makefile
!/package.json
!/package-lock.json

# 应用源码与 Docker 构建输入
!apps/
!apps/server/
!apps/server/**
!apps/hono/
!apps/hono/**
!apps/web/
!apps/web/**

# 排除依赖、构建、缓存、测试输出和本地环境
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
.next/
apps/web/.next/
apps/web/out/
apps/web/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
apps/hono/dist/
apps/server/tmp/
.nuxt/
.turbo/
.vercel/
dist/
build/
out/
coverage/
playwright-report/
test-results/
.cache/
tmp/
temp/
*.tsbuildinfo
*.test
*.out
coverage.out
lirs-api
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.eslintcache
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# 操作系统和编辑器噪音
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.idea/
.vscode/
.gitattributes
.envrc
*.swp
*.swo
*~
